metadata.name: MORBS™ - Baby Krypto
metadata.description:
Baby Krypto is running wild int he QUANTUM lab facility, driving the Mutant engineers crazy. Catch him before it too late!

MORBS™ new ETH NFT series featuring all the characters created by NiftyBC in his WAX Blockchain Augmented reality series. Revisiting the lore and backstory and gearing up for some really fun airdrops and IRL collectibles.
